 * HapticClient.cpp
 * ================
 * CLIENT side – runs on PC-B (has Novint Falcon #2).
 *
 *   1. Listens on 0.0.0.0:4000 for HapticPacket from server
 *   2. Applies received server position as force feedback (if FB on)
