 *   T   toggle TX (send back to server)
 *   R   toggle RX (receive from server)
 *   F   toggle force-feedback to local Falcon
 *   X   toggle X-axis (transmit + chart)
 *   Y   toggle Y-axis
 *   Z   toggle Z-axis
 *   +/- candle window finer/coarser
 *   [   set candle window to minimum (1 ms)
 *   ]   set candle window to maximum (1 s)
 *   ESC quit
 *
 * *** SET SERVER_IP BEFORE BUILDING ***
 */

